NeoPanel Android ELF

This project is an Android root ELF port and custom panel implementation built with EUI-NE rendering concepts and primitives.

Required upstream attribution:

https://github.com/sudoevolve/EUI-NE

Active Git submodule remote:

https://github.com/sudoevolve/EUI-NEO

The local upstream EUI-NE source used during development carried an Apache License 2.0 LICENSE file. Verify the current upstream license before public redistribution.

The Android ELF Port Kit files under third_party/eui-neo-android-elf-port-kit document and provide Android Surface, Vulkan, and input integration used by this project.
